        "liquid_76nQtp": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "settings": {
            "liquid": "<!--\n  Bloc éditorial / bénéfice à placer sous le titre du produit.\n  Compatible avec un bloc \"Liquid personnalisé\" Shopify.\n\n  Pour utiliser une vraie photo à gauche :\n  1. Remplacez le bloc .product-quote-benefit__avatar-icon par une balise <img>.\n  2. Exemple :\n     <img class=\"product-quote-benefit__avatar-image\"\n          src=\"URL-DE-VOTRE-IMAGE\"\n          alt=\"Parent satisfait\">\n-->\n\n<style>\n  .product-quote-benefit {\n    --quote-text-color: #3f3f3f;\n    --quote-muted-color: #929292;\n    --quote-accent-color: #1299f5;\n    --quote-avatar-background: #f4efe8;\n    --quote-font-size: 14px;\n    --quote-meta-size: 12px;\n    --quote-avatar-size: 48px;\n\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 12px 0 16px;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit,\n  .product-quote-benefit * {\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__inner {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: var(--quote-avatar-size) minmax(0, 1fr);\n    gap: 12px;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__avatar {\n    display: grid;\n    width: var(--quote-avatar-size);\n    height: var(--quote-avatar-size);\n    place-items: center;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    color: var(--quote-accent-color);\n    background: var(--quote-avatar-background);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__avatar-icon {\n    width: 62%;\n    height: 62%;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__avatar-image {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__content {\n    min-width: 0;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__text {\n    margin: 0;\n    color: var(--quote-text-color);\n    font-size: var(--quote-font-size);\n    font-weight: 400;\n    line-height: 1.35;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__text strong {\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__meta {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 6px;\n    margin-top: 7px;\n    color: var(--quote-muted-color);\n    font-size: var(--quote-meta-size);\n    font-style: italic;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__check {\n    display: grid;\n    width: 16px;\n    height: 16px;\n    flex: 0 0 16px;\n    place-items: center;\n    color: #ffffff;\n    background: var(--quote-accent-color);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n\n  .product-quote-benefit__check svg {\n    width: 62%;\n    height: 62%;\n  }\n\n  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n    .product-quote-benefit {\n      --quote-font-size: 13px;\n      --quote-meta-size: 11px;\n      --quote-avatar-size: 44px;\n      margin-top: 10px;\n      margin-bottom: 14px;\n    }\n\n    .product-quote-benefit__inner {\n      gap: 10px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"product-quote-benefit\" aria-label=\"Bénéfice du Cahier de Pratique Magique\">\n  <div class=\"product-quote-benefit__inner\">\n\n    <div class=\"product-quote-benefit__avatar\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n      <svg class=\"product-quote-benefit__avatar-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\">\n        <path d=\"M17 15H43C46.3 15 49 17.7 49 21V49H21C17.7 49 15 46.3 15 43V17C15 15.9 15.9 15 17 15Z\"\n              fill=\"currentColor\" opacity=\"0.16\"/>\n        <path d=\"M20 13H44C47.3 13 50 15.7 50 19V46C50 47.7 48.7 49 47 49H22C18.7 49 16 46.3 16 43V17C16 14.8 17.8 13 20 13Z\"\n              stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <path d=\"M24 23H42M24 30H42M24 37H36\"\n              stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        <path d=\"M16 43C16 39.7 18.7 37 22 37H50\"\n              stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"product-quote-benefit__content\">\n      <p class=\"product-quote-benefit__text\">\n        Un cahier <strong>ludique, effaçable et réutilisable</strong> pour aider votre enfant à mieux contrôler son stylo, développer sa motricité fine et progresser à son rythme.\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"product-q